Package: arcpt
Title: Changepoint Detection in Autoregressive Time Series
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Atharv", "Raskar", email = "atharv.raskar@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Claude", "Opus", role = "ctb",
           comment = "AI assistant for code development"))
Description: Detects changepoints in autoregressive (AR) time series using
    regression-based methods. Supports AR(1) and AR(2) models with optional
    trend components. Uses the PELT algorithm for efficient multiple
    changepoint detection. This package was developed as part of the GSoC 2026
    application for the "Generalized Changepoint Regression" project.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
